### Frontend Layer

#### [MODIFY] [index.html](file:///c:/Users/justi/Downloads/School%20Files/MainProjectCollection/ComprogStudies/ProjectsWebDev/Capstone%20Things/DeveloperVersion/frontend/index.html)

##### 1. Login Credentials & Role Labels
- Add `admin@hontech.com` / `admin123` quick-login card to the login screen.
- Update role label mappings:
  - `assistant` -> `Assistant Staff`
  - `sa` -> `Service Advisor`
  - `owner` -> `Owner`
  - `admin` -> `Admin`

##### 2. Navbar Realignment
- **Owner (`owner`)**: sees Analytics (`dashboard`), Records (`queue`), and My Profile.
- **Admin (`admin`)**: sees Staff Access (`staff`), Records (`queue`), and My Profile.
- **Assistant Staff (`assistant`)**: sees Online Booking (`intake`), Master Queue (`queue`), and TV Monitor link.
- **Service Advisor (`sa`)**: sees Walk-In Form (`intake`), Daily Intakes (`queue`), and TV Monitor link.

##### 3. TV Monitoring layout (Slide 2)
- Rearrange `tv-slide-2` columns:
  - Left column: Ready for Release (Top), Upcoming Vehicles (Bottom).
  - Right column: Carry-Over (Full Height).

##### 4. Table Columns & Controls
- **Goal column**:
  - Rename to "Service SLA (2h)" or "SLA Status" for a professional tone.
  - Hide this column entirely for `assistant` and `sa` roles. Keep it visible only for `owner` and `admin`.
- **Status & Location separation**:
  - Split "Status & Location" header and cells into two separate columns: "Status" and "Location".
  - **Location column**: Displays dropdown for Lifts (`None`, `Lift 1`, `Lift 2`, `Lift 3`, `Lift 4`).
    - If a Lift is occupied by another vehicle, color its dropdown option Red and append `(Occupied - [Plate])`.
    - If the row is assigned to a Lift, display the lift badge in a prominent orange/red color.
  - **Status column**:
    - For SA, displays a dropdown containing only: `Ready` (Released (Show TV)), `Released` (Released (Remove)), and `Carry Over`.
    - Read-only statuses like `Waiting` or `In Progress` are displayed as text.
- **Remarks & Actions**:
  - Separated into "Remarks/Reasons" and "Actions" columns.
- **Assistant Staff table restriction**:
  - For `assistant`, render all cells in the queue table as read-only text (using spans) *except* for the **Arrival** time field (which remains an editable `<input type="time">`). Disable all other select/input elements and hide action buttons (Claim, Release, Delete).

##### 5. Analytics Upgrades (Owners Module)
- Add a Branch selection filter (`All Branches`, `Branch A`, `Branch B`) to the dashboard.
- Display Branch-specific metrics and comparative visualizations.
- Add new **Efficiency & Volume Insights**:
  - **Average Turnaround Time (TAT)** (Arrival to Departure).
  - **Peak Intake Hours** (most frequent arrival hours).
  - **Walk-in vs. Online Booking Ratio**.
  - **SLA Violation Rate** (PMS exceeding 2h).

##### 6. Search Engine (Period Record Log Table)
- Implement a comprehensive search field that searches across Plate, Vehicle Model, Customer Name, Category, SA, Status, and Location in real-time.

